Summary: bright flashing at times almost fluttering at times moving very slow across sky
divs: sighting detailsi stepped out on back deck to have a smoke last night. it was a clear sky with stars shining. straight off my deck above tree line i saw the light. first thought it was a star but it appeared to be hovering\waving back n fourth very slowly up down and side to side. it seemed to be a long way away. and also fluttered lights that seem to change color or spin from time to time. i was shocked and just had to get witnesses so people didn think i was seeing things. i grabbed my girlfriend to see it and also went to get neighbor and the three of us watched it till it fell bleow tree line out of site. and it showed back up tonight but by the time i seen it it was rite at tree line and was gone within minutes. first seen it on 10\02\2011 at approx 7:50pm till shortly after 9pm we tried to get video but i dont think it turned out. im no expert on video though. i haven't tried veiwing on a large screen yet
